{"tid":2074464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗：將疑犯引渡至中国檢控和審訊理所當然 因中国政府擁有管轄權","createTime":"2020-06-22T06:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T13:01:24.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b82bbe21a9d76387d51e6934499eb4b8bcb0ff6e","tid":2074464,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗接受《有線新聞》訪問，談及港區国安法，重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻港區国安法用字為「顛覆國家政權」而非基本法廿三條的「顛覆中央人民政府」，即條文覆蓋顛覆香港特區政府的行為；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻港區国安法下中国駐港機關的管轄權包括執法、檢控和審批權，當香港情況已失控且行政長官要求即可動用；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻因中国政府擁有管轄權，將疑犯引渡至中国檢控和審訊自然是選項之一；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗聲稱行政長官選擇法官時的政治考量為法官本人有否曾表達立場，又指要相信香港法官。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：AFP記者Xinqi Su<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1274935657060642818?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxinqisu%2Fstatus%2F1274935657060642818%3Fs%3D12&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=47bcb12a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxinqisu%2Fstatus%2F1274935657060642818%3Fs%3D12&h=78f21e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1274935657060642818?s=12</a><br />\n<br />\n相關訪問：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/en-us/l/open-content?cid=28455&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fen-us%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D28455%26ct%3D1&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3a35f54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/en-us/l/open-content?cid=28455&amp;ct=1</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港政治<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26876&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=037d4b75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26876</a>"},{"pid":"549426df94c70f411a51f2fa0255c3988c8404dd","tid":2074464,"uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"cite